reviewText: Sid and Marty Krofft Collector's Edition Volume 10: Episodes on this volume include HR Pufnstuf: Horse with the Golden Throat, Lidsville: Let's Hear It For The Whizzo, Electra Woman and Dyna Girl: Return of the Sorcerer part 1, Sigmund and the Sea Monsters: Sweet Mama Redecorates, Lost Saucer: Beautiful Downtown Atlantis, Electra Woman and Dyna Girl: Return of the Sorcerer part 2. This is volume 10 of the Columbia House series.
